# Architecture

## RTL Architecture

The project implements a parameterized AMBA APB3-compliant Master-Slave communication system.

```text
                 +----------------+
                 |   APB Master   |
                 |----------------|
 User Control -->| start          |
                 | write          |
                 | addr           |
                 | wdata          |
                 +-------+--------+
                         |
                         | APB Bus
                         |
     +-------------------+-------------------+
     | PSEL                              PREADY
     | PENABLE                           PSLVERR
     | PWRITE                            PRDATA
     | PADDR
     | PWDATA
     v
                 +----------------+
                 |   APB Slave    |
                 |----------------|
                 | Memory Array   |
                 | Wait States    |
                 | Error Logic    |
                 +-------+--------+
                         |
                         v
                 +----------------+
                 | Internal Memory|
                 +----------------+
```

---

## APB Transfer Flow

```text
        IDLE
          |
          | start
          v
       SETUP
    PSEL = 1
 PENABLE = 0
          |
          v
      ACCESS
    PSEL = 1
 PENABLE = 1
          |
          | PREADY = 1
          v
        IDLE
```

---

## Master Architecture

### Responsibilities

- Generate APB read/write transactions
- Control APB protocol timing
- Drive APB bus signals
- Capture read data
- Report transaction completion
- Handle slave error responses

### Internal Blocks

```text
          +------------------+
          | FSM Controller   |
          +--------+---------+
                   |
      +------------+------------+
      |                         |
      v                         v
+------------+         +---------------+
| Address    |         | Data Register |
| Register   |         |               |
+------------+         +---------------+
      |                         |
      +------------+------------+
                   |
                   v
             APB Signals
```

---

## Slave Architecture

### Responsibilities

- Receive APB transactions
- Implement programmable wait states
- Perform memory read/write operations
- Generate PREADY response
- Generate PSLVERR for invalid accesses

### Internal Blocks

```text
             APB Interface
                    |
                    v
        +----------------------+
        | Wait-State Counter   |
        +----------+-----------+
                   |
                   v
        +----------------------+
        | Address Decoder      |
        +----------+-----------+
                   |
         +---------+---------+
         |                   |
         v                   v
    Memory Write       Memory Read
         |                   |
         +---------+---------+
                   |
                   v
                PRDATA
```

